Dea4epuE6T%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=acc6db2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20180517/hong-kong-journalist-detained-china/zh-hant/</a><br />\n巴打們點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf6d5ae6be254e8479ad90b1b9cbaf89b3d0962","tid":1465529,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"非法勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c56277c638534792d60bb800fb132f925b9f8d5","tid":1465529,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}